Some simple test code snippets related to the reapsberry
pi camera. Note: some if not all of the content was stolen 
from the internet.


0. install the camer following the instructions provided.
1. enable the camera:
    sudo raspi-config

2. test the camera:
    raspistill -o image.jpg

3. Install some python libraries (may already be there):
    sudo apt-get install python-picamera python3-picamera

4. Some python coding:
    timedsnap.py  timedvideo.py

5. In order to view the movies you created:
    cd Desktop
    omxplayer video.h264


